	</div>
	{{/sites}}
</div>

<div class="row">
	<div class="large-12 columns">
		<hr />
		<div class="panel">
			<h4>Tip: Use shortcut URLs!</h4>
					
			<p>Each site can be accessed through custom URLs. For example, to access the iOS developer portal, you can go to <a href="http://ios.{{{hostname}}}/">ios.{{{hostname}}}</a> or <a href="http://{{{hostname}}}/ios">{{{hostname}}}/ios</a>.</p>
		</div>
		
	</div>
</div>
